articles.title: Jaishankar meets new UK counterpart David Cameron, discusses West Asia, Ukraine conflict | Mint - Mint
articles.description: ‘Held a detailed discussion on realising the full potential of our strategic partnership,' the Indian foreign minister said following the meeting.
